JOHANNESBURG "All right stop! Collaborate and listen!"Music mash-up artist Swede Mason has compiled a hilarious video of the Game of Thrones cast singing lines from rapper Vanilla Ice s, classic song, "Ice Ice Baby".Mason is a renowned musician and video editor who gained fame for the mash-up, "Masterchef Synesthesia", in 2011.Click the video below to watch Jon Snow, Daenerys Targaryen and Tyrion Lannister, among others, perform the cheesy 1990 hit.The much-anticipated seventh season of Games of Thrones is set to premiere on 16 July.Since its debut in 2010, the fantasy epic has picked up 38 Emmys, more than any other fictional show in history, and has grown its audience in the US alone to more than 25 million.eNCA